<title>José Mauricio Nunes Garcia, Afro-Brazilian Composer & Organist</title>
<meta name="description" content="Padre José Mauricio Nunes Garcia (1767-1830) was an Afro-Brazilian composer and organist of liturgical music.  He was born September 22, 1767 at Rio de Janeiro, and died April 18, 1830.">
<meta name="keywords" content="Afro-Brazilian composer, Afro-Brazilian organist, Brazilian composer, Brazilian organist, chapel master, Rio de Janeiro">
